annotationA: Enhancer of yellow 1 is a TAF9 protein and a main component of the Transcription factor II D (TFIID) complex. TFIID is involved in recruiting the transcription machinery to core promoters and organizing specific enhancer-promoter interactions
annotationB: FI01013p; Sequence-specific DNA binding transcription factor activity; protein heterodimerization activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of transcription, DNA-templated; transcription initiation from RNA polymerase II promoter
